---

Anthropic CEO Dario Amodei outlines an optimistic, realistic vision of what powerful AI could achieve for humanity across biology, poverty alleviation, neuroscience, and democratic governance.

### Highlights
* **Biology & Health:** Compressing 50–100 years of biological progress into 5–10 years.
* **Neuroscience:** AI-accelerated understanding of mental health and brain mechanics.
* **Global Economic Growth:** Deploying technology to bridge healthcare and economic disparities in developing nations.
